snippet.title: Terror of Hemasaurus - Development highlights #5
snippet.description:
Sign up for the beta!
https://hemasaurus.com/beta

Wishlist now to be notified upon release:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1016180/Terror_of_Hemasaurus/


A retro city smash 'em up with satisfying destruction physics. Play as Giant Monsters unleashing terror upon mankind in this modern arcade experience with the action turned up to eleven.

A Game by Loren Lemcke. Music by Shawn Daley.
